Question: Show all students who scored above 90
SQL: SELECT * FROM students WHERE name LIKE '%Show all students who scored above 90%';

Question: Show me all students
SQL: SELECT * FROM students WHERE name LIKE '%Show me all students%';

Question: List courses taught by Professor X
SQL: SELECT * FROM students WHERE name LIKE '%List courses taught by Professor X%';

Question: Get students enrolled in course Y
SQL: SELECT * FROM students WHERE name LIKE '%Get students enrolled in course Y%';
